description: Fishin' Ships is bringing you Portland's finest fish & chips, straight from the ocean to a curb near you! Locally sourced fish battered in locally brewed beer, these delicious dishes are really giving you a taste of fresh, local fare. Whether it's their signature fish & chips, fish tacos, curry-fish slider, or any of their other scrumptious seafood delights, Fishin' Ships is bringing you the very best in every single bite!
name: Fishin' Ships
